About us


 Giant Power Group adhere to management principle of pursuing civilization and creating brilliant, was founded in Oct.1991 with capitalization USD 15 million. Which consist of Head Office in Taipei of Taiwan, HK office and GP China factory Giant Power enterprise CO.,LTD.
Giant Power enterprise CO.,LTD is the main production base and was established in Aug.2005 with registered capital USD 6.5 million. It located in Guanghui Industrial Area, Dong Cheng Tech. Park, Dong Cheng District, Dong Guan City, Guangdong Province of China where occupied area is 10,800 ㎡ with employees 600. 
