Competitions[edit]




Giant banners in Mashhad Samen Velodrome


Giant currently sponsors international cycling teams. The most famous are the Team Sunweb team and the Global Giant Mountain Bike Team, as well as many national teams.
past sponsorship first team was Team ONCE ONCE (cycling team)#Team name from 1999 to 2003
ONCE & Giant help developed Mike Burrows designer Mike Burrows compact frame and originally only 3 sizes (S, M, L).
after as Team Telecom [1] 2004 - 2006 [2] HTC–Highroad#/media/File:T-Mobile team TDF 2004.jpg HTC–Highroad#/media/File:Serhiy Honchar - prolog TdF 2006.jpg
HTC Highroad was left of the doping scandal behind of the time & decided to continue with T-Mobile money but no naming rights. 2007-2008 HTC–Highroad [3]
and continued.
