					Full Description



		GIANT MANUFACTURING CO., LTD is principally engaged in the manufacture and distribution of bicycles and related accessories. The Company’s bicycle products consists of race bicycles, road bicycles, urban bicycles, mountain bicycles, folding bicycles, touring bicycles, sports bicycles, bicycles for women and children, as well as electric bicycles, among others. It also involves in the provision of bicycle components. The Company distributes its products within domestic market and to overseas markets, covering the Americas, Europe, Asia and other markets.
» Full Overview of 9921.TW







